<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182906>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25 – 32. Triplectides noumeiensis, new species, male holotype. 25, forewing; 26, hind wing; 27, forewing anastomosis detail; 28, genitalia, lateral; 29, genitalia, dorsal; 30, genitalia, ventral; 31, phallus, lateral; 32, phallus, ventral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182906/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182915>
    dc:description "FIGURES 92 – 94. Maps of Grande Terre, New Caledonia, with male Triplectides specimen records plotted. 92, Triplectides noumeiensis, new species; 93, Triplectides tigrinus, new species; 94, Triplectides koghiensis, new species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182915/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

